LMS class layout:
=================
LMS:						Login(), Run(), Load(), Save(), Quit()
----
Librarian* 					m_librarian;
Borrower*					m_borrower;


Borrower:					SearchBook(), Borrow(), Return(), BorrowerReport(), SetPass()
---------
BorrowerRecord* 			m_record;
BookRecordContainer* 		m_books;


Librarian:					AddBook(), RemoveBook(), AddBorrower(), RemoveBorrower(), SearchBook(), SearchBorrower(),
----------					Borrow(), Return(), BorrowerReport(), BorrowerReportAll(), BookReport, BookReportAll(),
							SetPass(), QuitLMS()

BorrowerRecordContainer* 	m_borrowers;							
BookRecordContainer* 		m_books;


BookRecordContainer:		Add(), Remove(), Search(), Report(), ReportAll()
--------------------



BorrowerRecordContainer:	Add(), Remove(), Search(), Report(), ReportAll()
------------------------


BookRecord:					GetTitle(), GetAuthor(), GetISBN(), GetStatus(), AddCopy(), RemoveCopy(), ReportAllBorrowers()
-----------


BorrowerRecord:				GetName(), GetPhoneNum(), GetID(), AddBorrowed(), RemoveBorrowed(), ReportAllBorrowed()
---------------





















UI:				PromptUser(), RunLibrarian(), RunBorrower(),  
Library*				m_bookRecords;
